46
00:03:56,040 --> 00:03:57,240
because of Che.

47
00:03:57,960 --> 00:03:58,800
Yes.

48
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,320
I want you to die so that

49
00:04:00,320 --> 00:04:02,040
Yanyu can have another wife
and another son,

50
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:03,560
and I'll get Che's custody.

51
00:04:04,840 --> 00:04:06,480
Everyone

52
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,480
in the Zhou's Mansion

53
00:04:08,920 --> 00:04:10,040
