want to have a child with me?

61
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,600
I know you're upset.

62
00:04:32,280 --> 00:04:33,600
If you help me,

63
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,840
I'll do anything for you.

64
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,320
Okay.

65
00:04:42,320 --> 00:04:43,480
Then kneel down

66
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:45,400
and kowtow to me 100 times.

67
00:04:46,120 --> 00:04:47,440
Maybe I'll help you

68
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:48,880
when I'm satisfied.

69
00:05:06,360 --> 00:05:07,360
Lady Lu said

70
00:05:07,360 --> 00:05:08,440
no matter what happens,

71
00:05:08,440 --> 00:05:09,840
you must stay calm.

72
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,080
Enough.

73
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,200
Remember,

74
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:05,480
I'm doing this

75
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:08,160
for Che.

76
00:06:18,760 --> 00:06:21,040
I'll definitely pay you back.

77
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,000
Dad!

78
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:39,040
Dad!

79
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:40,800
