102
00:07:37,320 --> 00:07:38,160
Orphan Cave.

103
00:07:40,120 --> 00:07:42,000
Don't be scared. I'll look for him.

104
00:07:44,160 --> 00:07:45,200
I'll go with you.

105
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:52,960
